9a8618a1295a4031f3738a3a9a3fae1a3de51df6379b5820b0552e464333af8196426a1f5183e511801d99638d6d52ccb3e9c1ae2cfb21adea90a979c4a0ddfb  s390x-allow-generic-build.patch
2b6d9385a47d88df99a4b8de27bb07aa1205ea2fe188042aa25c21ae66aaae652bfb43637363589bb7f06664bd0c15ae977cbedaff80b8f98b64290ca09a4618  musl-fix-GLIBC_PREREQ.patch"
